data.description: Quietly nestled in a Cul-de-sac this AMAZING move in ready home has your wish list checked off! Fresh paint through out this 4 bedroom 2 full bath home. Main living area recently updated with an electric fire place, and reinforced backing to hang your extra large TV. Located in sequoyah school district this home offers a large living room, with a flex room directly off the kitchen that can be used for game room or a second living area, galley style kitchen, two pantries, and wash room off large sun room. A 24x40 Shop with a personal work room in the back that is insulated for heat and cold depending on the weather for your working needs, along with a 12x16 storage shed, tornado shelter, as sitting on over and acre! Don't miss your opportunity to check out this amazing home!
